.aider*
.vscode/
outputs/
*.wav

# trame-sonore-ia: allow small derived artefacts to be tracked.
# All audio (wav) stays ignored via the *.wav rule above; only the
# JSON of EMD-derived chords, the report figures, and the delivered PDFs
# are committed alongside the source code.
!trame-sonore-ia/outputs/
trame-sonore-ia/outputs/*
!trame-sonore-ia/outputs/depth_harmonies.json
!trame-sonore-ia/outputs/report_figs/
!trame-sonore-ia/outputs/report_figs/*.png
!trame-sonore-ia/outputs/Symphonie_Arctique_Trame_Sonore_IA_v1.pdf
!trame-sonore-ia/outputs/Soil_Audio_Methods_Report_v4.pdf
